To make the website more screen-friendly, I'll introduce some responsive design techniques using media queries. This ensures that the website layout adapts gracefully to different screen sizes.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cricket Club - Home</title>
    <style>
        /* CSS for basic styling */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        nav {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #fff;
            margin: 0 5px;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #555;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .form-container {
            display: none;
            width: 40%;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        input[type="text"], input[type="password"], input[type="submit"], input[type="email"], input[type="date"], select {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        input[type="submit"] {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        input[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #555;
        }

        /* CSS for additional content */
        .welcome-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .welcome-section h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .about-cricket {
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .about-cricket img {
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 400px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .about-cricket p {
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .card-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 300px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 20px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        /* Media queries for responsiveness */
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .form-container {
                width: 80%;
            }
            .about-cricket img {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .form-container {
                width: 90%;
            }
            .card {
                flex: 1 1 90%;
                max-width: 90%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
